title: Big Jay & The Beastmaster Justin Silver Contemplate Dinosaurs & Rich Vos Complains About Complaining
description: Big Jay and guest host Justin Silver review the new Jurassic World movie, and how to best get your dinosaur on a plane. Plus, Rich Vos joins the show and discusses the trend of people who go to comedy clubs to complain. Finally, things get testy in the Bonfire studio as Big Jay and Christine and the crew get into a heated debate about pasta bowls.
author: podcasts@siriusxm.com (Comedy Central)
